    LoginAcceptedPacket
    The SoupTCP server sends a Login Accepted Packet in response to receiving a valid Login Request from the client.
    LoginRejectedPacket
    The SoupTCP server sends this packet in response to an invalid Login Request Packet from the client.
    LoginRequestPacket
    A Login Request Message is sent to the server immediately after the client tries to establish a connection to the server.
    LogoutRequestPacket
    Logout Request Message is used for sending a session termination request to the server.
